  "text": "The focus of this study is ODA, and so the study does not include aid from large private philanthropic organisations, such as the Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation. Data from philanthropic organisations are not reported to CRS. This kind of aid is also often not comprehensive or standardised, and sufficiently reliable data on disbursements to conflict-affected countries could not be found to include in the study [CITATION_1] .",
